OL,3,CMajor boost in bid for statue of
OL,4,Clegendary boxer Larry Gains
OL,6,FRun by his great-grandsons, they want
OL,7,Fto honour the boxer who fought and
OL,8,Ffound fame in Leicester in the 1930s.
OL,9,FHe moved to the city after growing up
OL,10,Fin Canada.
OL,12,FIn a letter to the foundation
OL,13,Fconfirming the approval, Leicester
OL,14,FCity Council wrote: "Larry was greatly
OL,15,Fadmired by the people of Leicester,
OL,16,Fhis adopted home.
