OL,3,CMajor boost in bid for statue of
OL,4,Clegendary boxer Larry Gains
OL,6,F"His inspiring story absolutely
OL,7,Fdeserves recognition through an
OL,8,Fappropriate piece of public art, which
OL,9,Fwill both raise awareness of his
OL,10,Fachievements and inspire new
OL,11,Fgenerations."
OL,13,FOne of Larry's great-grandsons,
OL,14,FMichael Gains told ITV News Central:
OL,15,F"I'm truly delighted that Leicester
OL,16,FCity Council has given approval for a
OL,17,Fstatue of my great-granddad. This is
OL,18,Fan incredible step toward honouring
OL,19,Fhis legacy and everything he gave to
OL,20,Fthe community.
