OL,3,CMajor boost in bid for statue of
OL,4,Clegendary boxer Larry Gains
OL,6,F"We're now waiting to hear back from
OL,7,Fthe Charity Commission, and once
OL,8,Fapproved, we can begin organising
OL,9,Ffundraising events here in Leicester
OL,10,Fto make this vision a reality."
OL,12,FThat statue would be across the road
OL,13,Ffrom the Welford Road Stadium and the
OL,14,Fformer Granby Halls. Gains won the
OL,15,FCommonwealth Heavyweight Title when he
OL,16,Fdefeated Phil Scott at the Welford
OL,17,FRoad Stadium in 1931.
