OL,3,CMajor boost in bid for statue of
OL,4,Clegendary boxer Larry Gains
OL,6,FHowever, the boxer was denied the
OL,7,Fchance to win a World Heavyweight
OL,8,FChampionship not because of his
OL,9,Fability but due to the colour of his
OL,10,Fskin.
OL,12,FThe then colour-bar prevented black
OL,13,Ffighters from competing for World
OL,14,FChampionships until it was lifted in
OL,15,F1937. But Larry's victories earned him
OL,16,Fa grand parade in Leicester. He was
OL,17,Feven the guest of honour at a
OL,18,FLeicester pageant.
