OL,6,FCurrently the only visible tribute of
OL,7,FLarry Gains in his second home is
OL,8,Fhidden away. It's on the site of his
OL,9,Fold training gym - the Jolly Angler
OL,10,Fpub in the outskirts of the City.
OL,12,FThe new statue would feature the names
OL,13,Fof boxers from around the East
OL,14,FMidlands who have championed the sport
OL,15,Fincluding Mick Greaves, Tony Sibson
OL,16,Fand Rendall Munroe.
